  <brief_title>Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics Study of Oral Salmon Calcitonin in Healthy Postmenopausal Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Double-Dummy, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Crossover Phase I Study Assessing Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of Two Different SMC021 0.8 mg Variants and the Effect of Timing of Drug Intake in Healthy Postmenopausal Women</official_title>
  <sponsors>
