  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a phase I study to analyze bioavailability and pharmacodynamic of two different
      variants of oral salmon calcitonin (SMC021) in postmenopausal women
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
